{"id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0007","text":"未必轉身安慰它 但卻暗中牽着它","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["矛盾","關懷"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["安慰","牽着"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,3,9,3,3,4,3,2,4,4,3,3,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mei6","bit1","zyun2","san1","on1","wai3","taa1","daan6","koek3","am3","zung1","hin1","zoek6","taa1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"未必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"轉身","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"安慰","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"它","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"暗中","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"牽着","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"它","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"『未必轉身安慰』與『暗中牽着』形成對比，表達了內心的矛盾：不願直接表達關懷，但又在暗地裏默默支持。"},"source":{"title":"影子的愛情故事","artists":["林峯"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Love Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1054","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0008","text":"誰又會叫背影拖得那麼黑","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦","拖累"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["背影","拖","黑"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,2,9,3,3,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["seoi4","jau6","giu3","bui6","jing2","to1","dak1","naa5","mo1","hak1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"叫","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"背影","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"拖","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"那麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"黑","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"延續『背影』的意象，『拖得那麼黑』強烈地描繪了痛苦、沉重和不見天日的感受。"},"source":{"title":"影子的愛情故事","artists":["林峯"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Love Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1054","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0009","text":"愛是日的月的光 我是誰的誰的影","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["對比","身份"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["光","影"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,2,2,3,2,3,3,5,2,0,3,0,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","si6","jat6","dik1","jyut6","dik1","gwong1","ngo5","si6","seoi4","dik1","seoi4","dik1","jing2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"日","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"月","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"光","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"誰","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"影","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"將『愛』比喻為『日』、『月』的光，而自己則是『誰的影』，形成強烈的光影對比，暗示了對方是主導者，自己是依附者。"},"source":{"title":"影子的愛情故事","artists":["林峯"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Love Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1054","prev_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5p6X5bOw_MTA1NA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
